    <apiVersion>62.0</apiVersion>
    <description>Autolaunched subflow: generates Post-Closing checklist items for an Asset in Deal. Following GT-23 / US-029 this is now invoked from the AiD Orchestrator at LOI Signed (same time as Pre-Closing) rather than at Deal Closed-Won. The &#39;Closed - Won&#39; trigger status string is retained as the internal identifier that maps to the Post-Closing phase inside pro_ChecklistAutoGenerator. If varAidId is blank the generator falls back to all active AiDs on the Deal.</description>
    <label>Auto Generate Post-Closing Items</label>
